name: Timothy Wyatt
text: 1st time experiencing GF pizza was in Anchorage, AK...1994.  By far a superior pie!!!  While visiting Lexington, we saw the sign and thought, No Freaking Way (PG version]!!!  Phenominal experience with the staff at this location and the pie was as we expected!!!  Wish we had a location in Tampa, FL!!!

name: Jp Quinlan
text: Decent food.  Slooooooow cashiers. Love to go here but I only have 30 minutes for lunch.

name: Amanda Preston
text: Godfathers Pizza is some of the best I've ever had, the pieces are very large so it doesn't take much to fill up. I also really like the greasiness of the pizza, not sure if that's just me but the greaser the better.

name: Desiree Groves
text: Big slices for a great price!

name: Rosemary Taylor
text: Good. Prepared as ordered on tim

name: John Chamness
text: Best pizza I ever had at a gas station convenient store.
